              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The 80.5-MeV proton beam had an average",
                "intensity of 14 nA and a burst width of delta t less",
                "700 ps at the magnetic beam swinger which was operated",
                "with deflection angles of 0,11,and 24 degrees,",
                "respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
