              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SCIN",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".  This allowed to measure the angular",
                "range from 0 to 144 degrees with five fixed detectors.",
                "The detector which was used to measure angles of 82-106",
                "degrees (lab. angle) required a 15-cm diameter",
                "collimator hole to be cut through 1.2 m of concrete",
                "shielding.",
                "The neutron detectors consisted of cylindrical cells",
                " (30.5 cm diam*20.3 cm) filled with the liquid",
                "scintillator BI501,with photomultiplier tubes RCA 8854.",
                "Elastically scattered protons were detected with a",
                "deltaE-E telescope consisting of plastic",
                "scintillators."
              ]
            }
          ],
